author: Glen Tickle
title: ‘Trumpa the Hutt’ Turns Jabba the Hutt Into Donald Trump in a Scene From Return of the Jedi
text:
“ Trumpa the Hutt ” by Evil Ice Cream Pictures combines the slimy lowlife Jabba the Hutt with President Donald Trump by altering a scene from Return of the Jedi with clips of Trump speaking.
We took a little piece of the president and a little piece of Jabba The Hutt and mixed them together and made a fun little video showing how or very hutt like president would operate in a galaxy far far away.
